{"TopicId":178294,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"About to purchase but.......","CreatedByName":"anoldgrumpytroll","CreatedById":191872,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-14T08:19:32Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"anoldgrumpytroll","CreatedById":191872,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-14T08:19:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nQuick question before I purchase KSP. I am on a 2018 MacBook Pro, not a pc. Will this game run smoothly on a Mac? Anything I should be aware of regarding this game on a Mac before I buy? Thanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-14T11:31:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome to the forum, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/191872-anoldgrumpytroll/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022191872\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/191872-anoldgrumpytroll/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@anoldgrumpytroll\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot a mac user myself however this is the thread you probably need:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed8429661656\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/166190-macos-users-please-read/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:228px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GearsNSuch","CreatedById":190371,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-14T12:09:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/191872-anoldgrumpytroll/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022191872\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/191872-anoldgrumpytroll/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@anoldgrumpytroll\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn my experience, the latest version of KSP works just fine on a 2012 bottom-of-the-line Mac Mini running High Sierra.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI believe the issue mentioned in the thread linked above was resolved when they updated to Unity 2017.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think you\u0027ll be okay. Enjoy!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-09-14T17:50:15Z\u0022 title=\u002209/14/2018 05:50  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 14, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by GearsNSuch\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}